00:11:51.760 --> 00:11:52.240
Anyway.

130
00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:56.320
The relationship between Ash and Eiji in Banana 
fish is a lot like that of Victor and Yuri  

131
00:11:56.320 --> 00:12:01.040
