save the life of the person he loves.

149
00:13:44.400 --> 00:13:51.120
Showing the audience that desperate times can make 
a criminal out of anyone. Even the most innocent,  

150
00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:56.240
sweet hearted boy in the world. Ash even gets 
angry with him when he does break the law, even  

151
00:13:56.240 --> 00:14:01.840
to rescue Ash, because he wants Eiji to keep being 
the good guy, and not get drawn into this world.

152
00:14:02.960 --> 00:14:08.960
Crime, for Ash, is a way of life. It’s how he 
survived as long as he has. And while a queer  

153
00:14:08.960 --> 00:14:13.360
protagnost being a violent criminal may have 
some suburban gays clutching their pearls,  

154
00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:17.920
