stood out to conservative Europe as there was a  

175
00:16:05.040 --> 00:16:08.320
degree of tolerance even within 
rural sections of the country.

176
00:16:08.320 --> 00:16:11.840
It’s hard to be proud of a national 
history that was established by a bunch  

177
00:16:11.840 --> 00:16:16.800
of bisexual senators and emperors 
and cling to casual homophobia.

178
00:16:16.800 --> 00:16:17.600
The real threat  

179
00:16:18.640 --> 00:16:23.600
