Or… something, something, hide your children.

180
00:16:23.600 --> 00:16:30.400
In a way… even in modern media, we… somewhat… 
continue to propagate that line of thinking.

181
00:16:30.400 --> 00:16:34.640
Though the clean, suburban-friendly gay dad 
may be the consencus media portrayal of gay  

182
