protect the wealthy from the poor.

546
00:46:17.200 --> 00:46:21.440
For instance, laws prohibiting theft really 
accomplish nothing to protect the poor.

547
00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:24.560
For most of human history, the concept of ‘owning’  

548
00:46:24.560 --> 00:46:29.520
‘property’ was something entirely foreign 
to MOST people. Everything a serf had was  

549
00:46:29.520 --> 00:46:34.080
