whose net-worth is measured in stocks and bonds.

556
00:47:05.760 --> 00:47:10.080
A legal system that is invested in 
pursuing the more peaceful means  

557
00:47:10.080 --> 00:47:14.960
of coexistence among it’s people would 
aim to ensure a distribution of privilege.  

558
00:47:15.680 --> 00:47:20.160
Rather than focusing on protecting those 
who have enough of a horde to protect.

559
00:47:20.880 --> 00:47:21.920
There’s that dragon again.

560
00:47:22.560 --> 00:47:25.680
That there are no laws against 
withholding wealth from the poor  

561
00:47:25.680 --> 00:47:30.880
is abundantly telling. In fact, something 
